What you need to know:

Milimani Law Courts chief magistrate Francis Andayi said a former ICEA manager, Lincolin Kivuti Njeru, stole the money, dismissing his defence that “it was an investment loss.”The court said the money deposited in the accounts of ICEA were withdrawn and deposited into the personal account of Mr Njeru.The offence took place between January 17, 2003 and September 20, 2005.